34// Generic script for handling item dummy effects which trigger another spell.
35class spell_item_trigger_spell : public SpellScriptLoader
36{
37 private:
38 uint32 _triggeredSpellId;
39
40 public:
41 spell_item_trigger_spell(const char* name, uint32 triggeredSpellId) : SpellScriptLoader(name), _triggeredSpellId(triggeredSpellId) { }
42
43 class spell_item_trigger_spell_SpellScript : public SpellScript
44 {
45 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_trigger_spell_SpellScript);
46 private:
47 uint32 _triggeredSpellId;
48
49 public:
50 spell_item_trigger_spell_SpellScript(uint32 triggeredSpellId) : SpellScript(), _triggeredSpellId(triggeredSpellId) { }
51
52 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
53 {
54 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_triggeredSpellId))
55 return false;
56 return true;
57 }
58
59 void HandleDummy(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
60 {
61 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
62 if (Item* item = GetCastItem())
63 caster->CastSpell(caster, _triggeredSpellId, true, item);
64 }
65
66 void Register() override
67 {
68 OnEffectHit += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_trigger_spell_SpellScript::HandleDummy, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
69 }
70 };
71
72 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override
73 {
74 return new spell_item_trigger_spell_SpellScript(_triggeredSpellId);
75 }
76};

147// 64411 - Blessing of Ancient Kings (Val'anyr, Hammer of Ancient Kings)
148enum BlessingOfAncientKings
149{
150 SPELL_PROTECTION_OF_ANCIENT_KINGS = 64413
151};
152
153class spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings : public SpellScriptLoader
154{
155 public:
156 spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings") { }
157
158 class spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings_AuraScript : public AuraScript
159 {
160 PrepareAuraScript(spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings_AuraScript);
161
162 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
163 {
164 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_PROTECTION_OF_ANCIENT_KINGS))
165 return false;
166 return true;
167 }
168
169 bool CheckProc(ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
170 {
171 return eventInfo.GetProcTarget() != nullptr;
172 }
173
174 void HandleProc(AuraEffect const* aurEff, ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
175 {
176 PreventDefaultAction();
177
178 int32 absorb = int32(CalculatePct(eventInfo.GetHealInfo()->GetHeal(), 15.0f));
179 if (AuraEffect* protEff = eventInfo.GetProcTarget()->GetAuraEffect(SPELL_PROTECTION_OF_ANCIENT_KINGS, 0, eventInfo.GetActor()->GetGUID()))
180 {
181 // The shield can grow to a maximum size of 20,000 damage absorbtion
182 protEff->SetAmount(std::min<int32>(protEff->GetAmount() + absorb, 20000));
183
184 // Refresh and return to prevent replacing the aura
185 protEff->GetBase()->RefreshDuration();
186 }
187 else
188 GetTarget()->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_PROTECTION_OF_ANCIENT_KINGS, SPELLVALUE_BASE_POINT0, absorb, eventInfo.GetProcTarget(), true, NULL, aurEff);
189 }
190
191 void Register() override
192 {
193 DoCheckProc += AuraCheckProcFn(spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings_AuraScript::CheckProc);
194 OnEffectProc += AuraEffectProcFn(spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings_AuraScript::HandleProc, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY);
195 }
196 };
197
198 AuraScript* GetAuraScript() const override
199 {
200 return new spell_item_blessing_of_ancient_kings_AuraScript();
201 }
202};

204// 8342 - Defibrillate (Goblin Jumper Cables) have 33% chance on success
205// 22999 - Defibrillate (Goblin Jumper Cables XL) have 50% chance on success
206// 54732 - Defibrillate (Gnomish Army Knife) have 67% chance on success
207enum Defibrillate
208{
209 SPELL_GOBLIN_JUMPER_CABLES_FAIL = 8338,
210 SPELL_GOBLIN_JUMPER_CABLES_XL_FAIL = 23055
211};
212
213class spell_item_defibrillate : public SpellScriptLoader
214{
215 public:
216 spell_item_defibrillate(char const* name, uint8 chance, uint32 failSpell = 0) : SpellScriptLoader(name), _chance(chance), _failSpell(failSpell) { }
217
218 class spell_item_defibrillate_SpellScript : public SpellScript
219 {
220 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_defibrillate_SpellScript);
221
222 public:
223 spell_item_defibrillate_SpellScript(uint8 chance, uint32 failSpell) : SpellScript(), _chance(chance), _failSpell(failSpell) { }
224
225 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
226 {
227 if (_failSpell && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_failSpell))
228 return false;
229 return true;
230 }
231
232 void HandleScript(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
233 {
234 if (roll_chance_i(_chance))
235 {
236 PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
237 if (_failSpell)
238 GetCaster()->CastSpell(GetCaster(), _failSpell, true, GetCastItem());
239 }
240 }
241
242 void Register() override
243 {
244 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_defibrillate_SpellScript::HandleScript, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_RESURRECT);
245 }
246
247 private:
248 uint8 _chance;
249 uint32 _failSpell;
250 };
251
252 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override
253 {
254 return new spell_item_defibrillate_SpellScript(_chance, _failSpell);
255 }
256
257 private:
258 uint8 _chance;
259 uint32 _failSpell;
260};

318 class spell_item_deviate_fish_SpellScript : public SpellScript
319 {
320 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_deviate_fish_SpellScript);
321
322 bool Load() override
323 {
324 return GetCaster()->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER;
325 }
326
327 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
328 {
329 for (uint32 spellId = SPELL_SLEEPY; spellId <= SPELL_HEALTHY_SPIRIT; ++spellId)

339 caster->CastSpell(caster, spellId, true, NULL);
340 }
341
342 void Register() override
343 {
344 OnEffectHit += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_deviate_fish_SpellScript::HandleDummy, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
345 }
346 };

354// 71610, 71641 - Echoes of Light (Althor's Abacus)
355class spell_item_echoes_of_light : public SpellScriptLoader
356{
357 public:
358 spell_item_echoes_of_light() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_item_echoes_of_light") { }
359
360 class spell_item_echoes_of_light_SpellScript : public SpellScript
361 {
362 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_echoes_of_light_SpellScript);
363
364 void FilterTargets(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
365 {
366 if (targets.size() < 2)
367 return;
368
369 targets.sort(Trinity::HealthPctOrderPred());
370
371 WorldObject* target = targets.front();
372 targets.clear();
373 targets.push_back(target);
374 }
375
376 void Register() override
377 {
378 OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_item_echoes_of_light_SpellScript::FilterTargets, EFFECT_0, TARGET_UNIT_DEST_AREA_ALLY);
379 }
380 };
381
382 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override
383 {
384 return new spell_item_echoes_of_light_SpellScript();
385 }

427// http://www.wowhead.com/item=47499 Flask of the North
428// 67019 Flask of the North
429enum FlaskOfTheNorthSpells
430{
431 SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_SP = 67016,
432 SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_AP = 67017,
433 SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_STR = 67018,
434};
435
436class spell_item_flask_of_the_north : public SpellScriptLoader
437{
438 public:
439 spell_item_flask_of_the_north() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_item_flask_of_the_north") { }
440
441 class spell_item_flask_of_the_north_SpellScript : public SpellScript
442 {
443 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_flask_of_the_north_SpellScript);
444
445 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
446 {
447 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_SP) || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_AP) || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_STR))
448 return false;
449 return true;
450 }
451
452 void HandleDummy(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
453 {
454 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
455 std::vector<uint32> possibleSpells;
456 switch (caster->getClass())
457 {
458 case CLASS_WARLOCK:
459 case CLASS_MAGE:
460 case CLASS_PRIEST:
461 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_SP);
462 break;
463 case CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT:
464 case CLASS_WARRIOR:
465 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_STR);
466 break;
467 case CLASS_ROGUE:
468 case CLASS_HUNTER:
469 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_AP);
470 break;
471 case CLASS_DRUID:
472 case CLASS_PALADIN:
473 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_SP);
474 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_STR);
475 break;
476 case CLASS_SHAMAN:
477 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_SP);
478 possibleSpells.push_back(SPELL_FLASK_OF_THE_NORTH_AP);
479 break;
480 }
481
482 caster->CastSpell(caster, possibleSpells[urand(0, (possibleSpells.size() - 1))], true, NULL);
483 }
484
485 void Register() override
486 {
487 OnEffectHit += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_flask_of_the_north_SpellScript::HandleDummy, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
488 }
489 };
490
491 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override
492 {
493 return new spell_item_flask_of_the_north_SpellScript();
494 }
